es.usc.citius.lab.joctomap.octree

Class JOctreeNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • es.usc.citius.lab.joctomap.util.NativeObject
      • es.usc.citius.lab.joctomap.octree.JOctreeNode

  • public class JOctreeNode
extends NativeObject
    Represents a node of the JOctree, which is identified with a unique JOctreeKey. The node contains information about the occupancy in a region of the map. Also, in unexplored regions of the map, there is no nodes to represent that region. Since this is a native object, it extends to NativeObject to store the pointer properly.
    Author:
    Adrián González Sieira <adrian.gonzalez@usc.es>
